    	<p style="width: 480px; top: 101px;">
    	  As a Product Manager in Consumer Electronics industry, I used to spend
 countless hours parsing demographics and research data with market
 researchers on our team. Key metrics involving my product vs. its direct
 competition are critical for forecasting product success and assessing how
 to secure it. Historically, we had made most of our decisions based on
 assumptions with very little direct evidence. Since finding Amplified
 Analytics, however, we have been able to use their Market Intelligence
 Analysis to get the exact information we need— what people who spend their
 money on products like ours have to say about their experiences. These
 specific measurements make it very easy for me and my team to focus on
 critical information. The cost savings, too, are staggering, as we’ve been
 able to shed hundreds of man hours in the process. Plus, we get the
 research results within 24 hours— it used to take us 3-4 times longer just
 to initiate a survey.  Amplified Analytics is win-win for us— it provides
 us with the reliable feedback from customer analysis that we need to grow
 our customer base and pick off the competition, while saving us time and
 money.
      </p>
      
